source.name: Hazmat Yearly Incident Summary Reports - Data Mining Tool
source.description: Series of Incident data and summary statistics reports produced which provide statistical information on incidents by type, year, geographical location, and others. The data provided is that from the Hazardous Materials Incident Report Form 5800.1
